These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, aconite
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard
1. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Flower   | zinnia  | aconite |
| Game     | billiard | mah-jongg  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, zinnia
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, mystery
1. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Flower    | marigold      | zinnia         |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, thai
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, october
1. the malaysian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Nationality   | thai | malaysian   |
| Birthday       | october  | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee
House: palace, tower
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Beverage   | mirinda  | coffee |
| House         | palace | tower    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-5::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, davidoff
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, journalist
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2    |
| Cigar      | vegafina | davidoff |
| Job   | journalist        | accountant  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-6::.
2 different games are played: chess, canasta
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, sailing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |
| Game        | canasta  | chess |
| Sport   | biathlon | sailing  |

 #################################

 
